## Examples  

 <span data-ttu-id="8259a-102">Następujące przykładowe używa <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Point4DConverter> struktury do przekonwertowania ciągu na <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Point4D> struktury.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8259a-102">The following sample uses a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Point4DConverter> structure to convert a string into a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Point4D> structure.</span></span>  

```csharp  
...  

// Converts a String to a Point4D using a Point4DConverter  
// Returns a Point4D.  

Point4DConverter p4DConverter = new Point4DConverter();  
Point4D point4DResult = new Point4D();  
string string4 = "10,20,30,40";  

point4DResult = (Point4D)p4DConverter.ConvertFromString(string4);  
// point4DResult is equal to (10, 20, 30)  

...  
```
